Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.36,0:01:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.31,0:01:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you pull a better face than that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.08,0:01:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.08,0:01:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.09,0:01:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a fever again?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.69,0:02:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.19,0:02:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Not like that... Not like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.23,0:02:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.12,0:02:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.09,0:02:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I still dreaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.92,0:02:37.43,Title,,0,0,0,,Sudden Downturn!\NThe First Date is the Beginning of Misfortune
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.56,0:02:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought my heart was going to burst.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.28,0:02:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't sleep at all last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.11,0:02:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, I'll die of heart failure, thanks to Otani.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.65,0:03:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa, do you have summer classes again today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.82,0:03:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You've really got to get it together, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.16,0:03:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Your future will be something to look forward to.{?}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.36,0:03:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just... no good without you, Koizumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.00,0:03:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So this and that really weren't dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.18,0:03:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you, some old geezer?\NYour bangs are completely flat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.58,0:03:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I was wearing a hat, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.05,0:03:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.05,0:03:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.49,0:03:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Good... morn...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.63,0:03:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.97,0:03:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha-What are you doing wearing that, you idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.47,0:03:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Then just when am I supposed to wear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.07,0:03:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.97,0:03:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.94,0:03:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Nobu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.31,0:03:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.14,0:04:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.98,0:04:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a cute necklace.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.61,0:04:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.22,0:04:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Ah, this is—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.99,0:04:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.82,0:04:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It was.. uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.16,0:04:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...a gift from God.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.46,0:04:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.56,0:04:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. You, come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.06,0:04:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You absolutely cannot tell those guys anything unnecessary, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.93,0:04:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,"Unnecessary"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.84,0:04:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A-About this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.21,0:04:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.24,0:04:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,"This and that"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.52,0:04:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh... That.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.72,0:04:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So like I said, just keep your mouth shut.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should I have to listen to your lecturing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.19,0:04:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not lecturing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.72,0:04:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't pull that face.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.43,0:04:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But... I'm really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.36,0:04:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I  just want to say so out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.07,0:04:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but I don't just want to tell Nobu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.57,0:05:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I want the whole world to know how happy I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.54,0:05:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...about this and that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.14,0:05:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.41,0:05:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.21,0:05:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.28,0:05:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Do whatever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.38,0:05:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.42,0:05:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.02,0:05:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.62,0:05:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.36,0:05:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I already told you! Nothing happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.33,0:05:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.53,0:05:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up. I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa, you got that necklace from Otani-kun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.61,0:05:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani bought it for me
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.77,0:05:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my! How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.77,0:05:40.41,Superscript,,0,0,0,,Otani\Nbought it for me
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.41,0:05:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Is that so? That's wonderful, Risa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.28,0:05:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What. When did he give it to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.68,0:05:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday, while you guys were watching the fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.26,0:05:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.49,0:05:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.46,0:05:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. Were you guys sneaking around doing things behind our backs?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.20,0:06:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.00,0:06:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he gave me a present,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.03,0:06:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,...and he said, "I'm just no good without you, Koizumi."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.57,0:06:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.18,0:06:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.71,0:06:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck is that "kyaah" about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I've been trying really hard, but now it's paying off...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.82,0:06:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,...and my dream is finally coming true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.79,0:06:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.62,0:06:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be. You worked really hard for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.76,0:06:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.70,0:06:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,All Hanshin-Kyojin are finally a couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.43,0:06:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a long wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.30,0:06:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not going out yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.97,0:06:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! What the heck?!\NDidn't he ask you out?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.51,0:06:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So... he just gave you a present?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.68,0:06:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I got more than just a present...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.45,0:06:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But let's just leave it at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.12,0:06:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.26,0:07:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? But Risa-chan, you said your dream came true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.69,0:07:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, not long ago he said...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.86,0:07:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,"I mean, suppose she was my girlfriend."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.76,0:07:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,"Then we'd have to kiss."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.00,0:07:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.00,0:07:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,"Even though the two of us are alone in this room right now, I don't feel a thing."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.38,0:07:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,...and stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.01,0:07:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But then yesterday, {\i1}that{\i0} happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.15,0:07:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It was no illusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.32,0:07:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What's "that"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.06,0:07:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.36,0:07:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,All of my hard work has paid off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.43,0:07:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.57,0:07:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Say whatever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.07,0:07:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I'll see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.60,0:07:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.55,0:07:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.55,0:07:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.18,0:08:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to go somewhere before going home?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.26,0:08:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,At this point it would be natural to jump straight into dating, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Koizumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.17,0:08:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.33,0:08:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot to give this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.74,0:08:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, take one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.94,0:08:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool! A ticket to the World Athletics Championships!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.64,0:08:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's the night of the finals!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.14,0:08:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,These tickets are really hard to get.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.08,0:08:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad's been itching to get one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.25,0:08:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing, Otani! Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.92,0:08:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job. Big man! Big man!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.05,0:08:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? I don't get you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.09,0:08:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're making me uneasy,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.99,0:08:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...so I'm gonna hold onto this for safekeeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.46,0:08:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Risa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.06,0:08:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It really is you, Risa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.43,0:08:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Ake-chi! Long time no see!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.60,0:08:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.77,0:08:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm great!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.44,0:08:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is a friend of mine from middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.77,0:08:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.11,0:09:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me this is your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.91,0:09:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no. We're just friends, just friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.28,0:09:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But he might be my boyfriend tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.72,0:09:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.56,0:09:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You always said you'd never go for a guy shorter than you, right Risa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.66,0:09:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.26,0:09:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I've got to get going. See you around!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.23,0:09:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, uh... see ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.80,0:09:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.21,0:09:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Are you angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.68,0:09:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.38,0:09:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I said that stuff about not wanting a boyfriend shorter than me a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.52,0:09:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I care about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.12,0:09:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.59,0:09:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You...! I'm...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.46,0:09:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.76,0:09:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter? I'm concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.07,0:09:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Be concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.83,0:09:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's the matter? Otani!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.65,0:10:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry! I'm really sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.85,0:10:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.75,0:10:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you are always like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.52,0:10:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, I'm always like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You make it sound like I'm always late!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.53,0:10:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late one in every three times we go somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.13,0:10:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just as bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.73,0:10:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna lecture me when you're the one who was late?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.30,0:10:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.87,0:10:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll treat you to something today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.85,0:10:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. Were you waiting long?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.45,0:10:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope. I just got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.12,0:10:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It should've been like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.59,0:10:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.56,0:10:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot my handbag!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.66,0:11:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I was in a rush...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.93,0:11:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.53,0:11:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot! The event is about to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.64,0:11:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But my purse is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.64,0:11:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... I have some change in my pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.84,0:11:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you, some old geezer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.48,0:11:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you on your way to go play Pachinko?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.31,0:11:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I wanted to get my bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.98,0:11:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. It'll be my treat today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.09,0:11:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.29,0:11:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Come one. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.93,0:11:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a good thing I held on to your ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.33,0:11:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Honi-san! Iwashi-san! Hurry! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.20,0:11:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.61,0:11:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll miss Murouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.61,0:11:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.64,0:11:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You there, get out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.41,0:11:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.91,0:11:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, you old bags?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.35,0:11:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing. Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.12,0:11:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.99,0:12:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.66,0:12:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.89,0:12:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.30,0:12:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I think my finger got cut by one of those women's handbags.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.23,0:12:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Just a minute. I have bandages.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I always keep some in my handb—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.77,0:12:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, that's right. I forgot my handbag.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.11,0:12:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That might Murouchi. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.33,0:12:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Murouchi is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.46,0:12:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He easily passed the 80 meter mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.50,0:12:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.37,0:12:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If Otani's ex-girlfriend, Kanzaki, was in that situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.77,0:12:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'm sure she would've pulled out a bandage right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.51,0:12:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,She was manager of the basketball team, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.05,0:12:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.28,0:12:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Or something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.05,0:13:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,She really was a sweet girl, that Kanzaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.39,0:13:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi, you've been sighing for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.59,0:13:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you having fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.73,0:13:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What? No. I'm having fun, I'm having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.06,0:13:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Murouchi about to start? I'm so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.60,0:13:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Come here for a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.37,0:13:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up with you? It's just a handbag.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.44,0:13:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.11,0:13:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for being like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.61,0:13:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.95,0:13:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you what bothered me last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.09,0:13:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.96,0:13:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Couldn't you have paused for a second before saying we were just friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.23,0:13:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about what I said when I bumped into Ake-chi back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.00,0:13:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Would friends do {\i1}that{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.31,0:13:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,"Тhat"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.51,0:14:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you honestly think I would do that with someone I considered "just a friend"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.15,0:14:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I would never kiss a girl who was just a friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.93,0:14:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.93,0:14:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.43,0:14:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,After kissing like that, we're not just friends, are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.70,0:14:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So... What am I to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.20,0:14:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.74,0:14:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But you never told me clearly. How should I know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.64,0:14:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You should know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.68,0:14:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.65,0:14:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The kiss alone was enough to make me happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.72,0:14:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I have done something like that for no reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.13,0:14:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It made me happy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.26,0:14:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.83,0:14:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to have you arrested for stealing my heart, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.37,0:15:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an illusion...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.44,0:15:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't cry, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.68,0:15:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.88,0:15:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.28,0:15:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I like you a lot, Otani!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.52,0:15:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.52,0:15:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I really, really love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.99,0:15:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm seriously in love with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.92,0:15:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.69,0:15:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.93,0:15:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.73,0:15:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.93,0:15:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.54,0:15:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And... you love me too, right, Otani?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.05,0:15:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job, buddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.82,0:15:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.36,0:16:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you thinking, saying all that in front of so many people?! Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.93,0:16:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But... I was just so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.30,0:16:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that ugly face of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.71,0:16:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't help it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.28,0:16:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You've stolen my heart, Otani.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.18,0:16:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh dear. I've stolen it, have I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.62,0:16:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.72,0:16:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to steal yours, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.22,0:16:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot. Mine isn't so easy to steal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.29,0:16:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thirsty. Go get me something to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.06,0:16:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Your choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.96,0:16:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You have change, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.97,0:16:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to steal my heart, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.81,0:16:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.31,0:16:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Off you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.34,0:16:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.65,0:16:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani sure is a nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.35,0:16:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm falling in love with him even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.59,0:17:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if he's really happy with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.63,0:17:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he did say "yeah."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.10,0:17:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This road has sure been long.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.67,0:17:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my first time experiencing requited love.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.60,0:17:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, we're gonna be all lovey-dovey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.01,0:17:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ot—!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.38,0:17:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.88,0:17:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the ex-girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.22,0:17:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Just now, was that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.47,0:17:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.64,0:17:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That looks like it hurts. Is it a blister?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.01,0:17:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... I'm not used to these shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.14,0:17:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you sit down over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.71,0:17:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a good thing I'm carrying bandages...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.35,0:17:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.88,0:18:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,She'd always carry bandages, wouldn't she...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.22,0:18:02.12,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Raise your foot a bit, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.59,0:18:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,She's such a sweet girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.39,0:18:05.89,Overlap,,0,0,0,,It's not too bad. You should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.06,0:18:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.56,0:18:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what's the matter? Does it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.73,0:18:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.53,0:18:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Atsushi-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.70,0:18:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,She got a blister, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.00,0:18:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Really? You should've said so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.20,0:18:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate this. I'm so embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.10,0:18:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so embarrassed right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.67,0:18:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't like a girl this embarrassing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.34,0:18:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd prefer Kanzaki-san to me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.41,0:18:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Kanzaki-san is still broken hearted after breaking up with her giant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.72,0:18:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Otani.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.55,0:18:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Our time was short, but it made me so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.69,0:18:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Kanzaki. I'll take it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.29,0:18:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Okay then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.40,0:18:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... sorry, what was your name again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.80,0:18:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi Risa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.07,0:18:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She's my girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.67,0:18:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.24,0:19:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. The giant's waiting for you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.31,0:19:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.59,0:19:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently she and the giant got back together so they came here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.39,0:19:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Good for her, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.93,0:19:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,"Girlfriend."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.03,0:19:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.40,0:19:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really okay with having a girlfriend like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.10,0:19:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.24,0:19:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, give me your foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.78,0:19:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This happened because you got carried away and wore clothes you're not used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.31,0:19:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But this... this is our first date.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.85,0:19:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to look cuter for you. At least just a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.96,0:19:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no. This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.13,0:19:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I think my heart was just stolen a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.13,0:19:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.26,0:19:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Just talking to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.00,0:20:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, I cried for ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.14,0:20:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of that, I couldn't see the World Championships through my tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.02,0:20:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Murouchi sure worked hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.35,0:20:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Are you still crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.42,0:20:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You look pitiful. Here, dry your tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.69,0:20:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart's been stolen again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.26,0:20:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Just how many hearts do you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.67,0:20:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're finally back to your usual self.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.17,0:20:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,A-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.87,0:20:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.88,0:20:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You came to watch, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.18,0:20:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I came with Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.55,0:20:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Woah! What a beautiful girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.88,0:20:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,"A-chan"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.88,0:20:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,"Mimi"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.52,0:20:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.39,0:20:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, she's my neighbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.02,0:20:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello! I'm Yoshioka Mimi. I'm in my second year of middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.19,0:20:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Middle school?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,She looks so mature!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.20,0:21:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.13,0:21:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A-chan, who's this? A friend of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.57,0:21:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.37,0:21:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.71,0:21:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.84,0:21:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,When did this happen?!\NThis is the first I've heard about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.38,0:21:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.38,0:21:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.92,0:21:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Your old man is waiting for you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.55,0:21:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Koizumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.75,0:21:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.12,0:21:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later, Mimi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.73,0:21:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not accept this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.60,0:21:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A lame girl like that is A-chan's girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.10,0:21:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I'll accept it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.12,0:23:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi, want to come study at my place?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.89,0:23:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure! This feels so lovey-dovey.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.76,0:23:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Mimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.66,0:23:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Lovely Complex ~ Love Com.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.60,0:23:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Next: Declaration of War!! The Dangerous Beauty Who Burns With Jealousy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.30,0:23:20.00,Preview Title,,0,0,0,,Declaration of War!! The Dangerous Beauty Who Burns With Jealousy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.00,0:23:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure to watch!
